{"tid":1561741,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唱歌=確立本土意識=走近成功","createTime":"2019-09-11T17:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T03:39:56.000Z","uid":274371,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd22fcdca6a49c52b068ceaf4c5f10a4d238fde","tid":1561741,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:01:47.000Z","msg":"見到有人講大家唔好重覆犯錯，好似2014咁唱今天我就了事。我唔同意，因為《願榮光歸香港》直接<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">（係直接呀！！！）</span>確立香港人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本土、自治嘅意識</span></span>，將本來唔易入口嘅內容，化為最入屋嘅歌聲，連<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">淺黃都拉到變深黃</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n明白大家都係怕個運動會完，但我向你保證，唱《願榮光歸香港》只會為運動帶來<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>正面影響</strong></span>，越唱，香港人嘅自我意識越強。越唱，大家越肯願意為香港繼續走出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n的確，除咗《願榮光歸香港》，我哋仲需要更多方法對抗呢個政權，我哋繼續一齊努力啦，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山<br />\n各自努力</span></span>"},{"pid":"d7c96cd63d61f66c1889dc324a2915a7b619633e","tid":1561741,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"0d02e591fbe80c08c65f6548ffce88efceab23a3","tid":1561741,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:02:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=